name: Neapolis
summary:
🏛️ Explore. Survive. Uncover the Lost City.

Neapolis is a cinematic VR adventure where ancient myths come to life beneath the modern world.
Play solo or co-op, explore hidden ruins, solve ancient puzzles, and communicate via voice or text chat as you uncover the secrets buried below.

🧭 Immersive Exploration – Walk through vast, mysterious worlds.

🧩 Puzzles & Secrets – Ancient enigmas reveal the city’s forgotten history.

🎧 Voice & Text Chat – Speak and strategize naturally with your team.
